description: Green Landscaping Group AB provides landscaping services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 1,373 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-03-23. The Company’s operations are divided into three business segments: Greenery and fine planning, Sports and leisure facilities, as well as Wood and forestry. Also, the Company operates Green Academy for employees’ skills development. The firm operates through a number of subsidiaries, active throughout the central and southern Sweden.
name: Green Landscaping Group AB
